{"tid":2057082,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為進一步鬆綁   MatePad Pro 美國零件只佔 2%","createTime":"2020-06-09T06:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T00:24:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c30f36a8fe7a79b8822b15a51971d61402369d20","tid":2057082,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"自從華為被美國商務部納入實體清單，禁止美國企業向其提供產品和技術後，就有更多人注意他們的手機和平板產品，到底零件來自什麼國家。最近大陸傳媒報導指早前上市 MatePad Pro 平板，來自美國的零件數量只有 2%。<br />\n<br />\n在拆開這部華為旗艦級平板後，發現零件如要來自中國大陸和日本廠商，亦有韓國、德國、荷蘭和奧地利供應商的零件。將 MatePad Pro 仔細拆解後共得出 1,411 件零件，當中來自日本的有 1,148 件，佔整體 81.4%，但成本則只佔 4.6%；韓國提供的零件只有 3 件，佔整體 0.2%，但成本佔 15.7%。由中國提供的零件有 225 件，佔整體 15.9%，成本卻佔 71%。"},{"pid":"056ba6e63a97cb52e55a0583a1259d38c808bf3c","tid":2057082,"uid":15564,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:43:51.000Z","msg":"等睇無左個2%連機都開唔到"},{"pid":"41d39a67f1d18963eefeab1876e0dd2a449ff248","tid":2057082,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/pad/talk/4472/68678/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fpad%2Ftalk%2F4472%2F68678%2F1%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=a6860cdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/pad/talk/4472/68678/1/</a>"},{"pid":"dab94721d8f87e55b9e6fa668ac7aede187371ed","tid":2057082,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"2% 晶片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e747960ff1ddf924b179cbefebaa9a9ecbc25e","tid":2057082,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:47:06.000Z","msg":"用mass計嘅2%?"},{"pid":"a4a85e3fe36d4e53e207dfd38793c8166ec8cca2","tid":2057082,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/pad/img/202